reat since Triesman began work.   Arsenal recruit   London: Arsenal have signed France rsquo;s Mikael Silvestre from Manchester United, the London Premier League club said on Wednesday. Silvestre became the first player to move from United to Arsenal in more than 30 years when he agreed a two-year contract with the London club.
                                                                                                                                                               
